com.nokia.places.request

Interface Request

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CategoryRequest, EditorialPageRequest, GeocodeRequest, PlaceRequest, ResultPageRequest, ReverseGeocodeRequest, ReviewPageRequest, SuggestionRequest

    public interface Request
    This interface forms the basis of all request classes, and allows the user to cancel asynchronous requests.
